summary:
Blueback: Sharing the Secrets - An interactive, behind-the-scenes look at the making of the film, Blueback.

 School Holiday Activities - Dive into the holidays with Ocean Superheroes: Explore, learn and unleash your inner hero at the Maritime Museum.

 Octopus Garden - Get tentacle-tied with this fascinating interactive experience.

 Ocean Photographer of the Year - World premier exhibition featuring over 100 photographs from some of the world’s best ocean photographers.

 Valerie Taylor: An Underwater Life - Dive into the remarkable world of an Australian marine pioneer!
